UID:p5Ez17vj3NDxhqf5bc97A
SUMMARY:Cascade Centennial Chapter\, SAR Monthly Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260322T022257Z
DTSTART:20260404T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Serving east king county The Cascade Centennial Chapter is loca
	ted in the Bellevue area \\(Seattle Eastside\\) and has approximately 100 
	members.  We meet at Enzo's Bistro in Issaquah on the first Saturday of th
	e month except for July\, August\, and September when we break for the sum
	mer.  Our meetings begin at 11am and end at 1pm\, and consist of opening c
	eremonies\, new member inductions and member awards\, lunch \\(order from 
	menu\\) and camaraderie\, a program pertaining to American Revolution hist
	ory\, chapter business\, and our closing ceremony.  Our flagship event is 
	our annual Veterans Day Ceremony which has evolved into one of the largest
	 in the State.  We welcome visitors\, and hope you'll join us! RSVP: https
	://www.washingtonsar.org/chapters/cascade-centennial/ For more information
	: https://www.wassarccc.org\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detai
	ls/cascade-centennial-chapter-sar-monthly-meeting/18306071/2026-04-04T00\n
	\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/cascade-centennial-chapte
	r-sar-monthly-meeting/18306071/2026-04-04T00
LOCATION:Enzo's Bistro & Bar\, 120 NW Gilman Blvd\, Issaquah\, WA
